query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from question AS q
inner join tag_question AS tq
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.favorite_count >= 0 AND q.favorite_count <= 10000
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('stackoverflow')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('android-service',
'c#-3.0',
'carousel',
'celery',
'controls',
'dynamics-crm-2011',
'el',
'focus',
'html-select',
'http-status-code-404',
'owin',
'preg-replace',
'sequence');
